              <div class="text">
                <div>
                  <h1>Shop Around</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="gold-border"></div>
                <div class="paragraph">
                  <p>
                    The primary goal with this project was clear from the start: enable online visitors to easily find and browse products, and then purchase these products, either online, or from a local retailer. Depth developed a responsive website that handles all the product variations, supports multiple currencies, and integrates with local brick-and-mortars to make sure a customer is always only a click (or a quick drive) away from the product.                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
