              <div class="text-wrapper">
                <div class="text">
                  <div>
                    <h1>Content Management</h1>
                  </div>
                  <div class="gold-border"></div>
                  <div class="paragraph">
                    <p>
                      Descente offers a wide array of products in different categories, and each product contains a host of variations, and this product line changes frequently. We developed a backend admin that enables Descente to easily manage and update this data, and since oftentimes the entire product line is changing, we created a seamless process to batch upload an entire set of new products.                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
